#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/software_setup.rst:2
msgid "Software Setup"
msgstr "软件设置"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/software_setup.rst:4
msgid ""
"Before you can start using your OpenMV Cam you'll need to download and "
"install `OpenMV IDE <https://openmv.io/pages/download/>`_."
msgstr ""
"在您开始使用 OpenMV Cam 之前，您需要下载并安装 `OpenMV IDE <https://openmv."
"io/pages/download/>`_。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/software_setup.rst:8
msgid "Windows"
msgstr "Windows"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/software_setup.rst:10
msgid ""
"OpenMV IDE comes inside of an installer that will automatically install "
"the IDE along with drivers for the OpenMV Cam and the MicroPython "
"pyboard. Just follow the default installer prompts."
msgstr ""
"OpenMV IDE 包含在一个安装程序中，该安装程序将自动安装 IDE 以及 OpenMV Cam 和 "
"MicroPython pyboard 的驱动程序。只需按照默认的安装程序提示操作即可。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/software_setup.rst:14
msgid ""
"To launch OpenMV IDE afterwards just click on its shortcut in the Start "
"Menu."
msgstr "要在之后启动 OpenMV IDE，只需单击“开始”菜单中的快捷方式。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/software_setup.rst:17
msgid "Mac"
msgstr "Mac"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/software_setup.rst:19
msgid ""
"OpenMV IDE comes in a ``.dmg`` file. Simply open the ``.dmg`` file and "
"then drag the OpenMV IDE ``.app`` onto the Applications folder shortcut "
"to install OpenMV IDE."
msgstr ""
"OpenMV IDE 以 ``.dmg`` 文件形式提供。只需打开 ``.dmg`` 文件，然后将 OpenMV "
"IDE ``.app`` 拖放到 Applications 文件夹快捷方式中以安装 OpenMV IDE。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/software_setup.rst:23
msgid ""
"In addition to installing OpenMV IDE you'll also want to install device "
"firmware update (DFU) support so that you can recover your OpenMV Cam if "
"you encounter a problem with our boot-loader."
msgstr ""
"除了安装 OpenMV IDE 外，您还需要安装设备固件更新（DFU）支持，"
"以便在我们的引导加载程序出现问题时可以恢复您的 OpenMV Cam。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/software_setup.rst:27
msgid ""
"First you'll need to install a package manager. Either `MacPorts "
"<https://www.macports.org/install.php>`_ or `HomeBrew "
"<http://brew.sh/>`_. If you don't have a preference choose HomeBrew."
msgstr ""
"首先，您需要安装一个软件包管理器。可以选择 `MacPorts <https://www.macports."
"org/install.php>`_ 或 `HomeBrew <http://brew.sh/>`_。如果没有偏好，请选择 "
"HomeBrew。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/software_setup.rst:31
msgid "For MacPorts you'll need to execute the following commands::"
msgstr "对于 MacPorts，您需要执行以下命令::"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/software_setup.rst:36
msgid "For HomeBrew you'll need to execute the following commands::"
msgstr "对于 HomeBrew，您需要执行以下命令::"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/software_setup.rst:41
msgid "In general, you have to install ``libusb``, ``python``, and ``pyusb``."
msgstr "一般来说，您需要安装 ``libusb``、``python`` 和 ``pyusb``。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/software_setup.rst:43
msgid ""
"To launch OpenMV IDE just click on its ``.app`` file in your Applications"
" folder."
msgstr "要启动 OpenMV IDE，只需单击 Applications 文件夹中的 ``.app`` 文件。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/software_setup.rst:47
msgid "Linux-Desktop"
msgstr "Linux-Desktop"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/software_setup.rst:49
msgid "OpenMV IDE comes inside of an installer ``.run`` file. Just do::"
msgstr "OpenMV IDE 包含在一个安装程序 ``.run`` 文件中。只需执行以下命令::"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/software_setup.rst:54
msgid ""
"And then follow the installer prompts to install OpenMV IDE on linux. "
"Afterwards, see the ``README.txt`` file and the ``setup.sh`` file in the "
"installer output directory for installing device firmware update (DFU) "
"support so that you can recover your OpenMV Cam if you encounter a "
"problem with our boot-loader."
msgstr ""
"然后按照安装程序提示操作在 Linux 上安装 OpenMV IDE。安装完成后，"
"请查看安装程序输出目录中的 ``README.txt`` 文件和 ``setup.sh`` "
"文件，以安装设备固件更新（DFU）支持，"
"以便在遇到我们的引导加载程序问题时可以恢复您的 OpenMV Cam。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/software_setup.rst:60
#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/software_setup.rst:85
msgid ""
"Finally, to launch OpenMV IDE just click on the ``bin/openmvide`` file. "
"If OpenMV IDE fails to launch you may need to add execution permissions "
"first. Do::"
msgstr ""
"最后，要启动 OpenMV IDE，只需单击 ``bin/openmvide`` 文件。如果无法启动 "
"OpenMV IDE，您可能需要先添加执行权限。执行以下命令::"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/software_setup.rst:67
#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/software_setup.rst:92
msgid "If this doesn't work then use the ``openmvide.sh`` script instead. Do::"
msgstr "如果这不起作用，则使用 ``openmvide.sh`` 脚本。执行以下命令::"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/software_setup.rst:72
#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/software_setup.rst:97
msgid ""
"In general, you'll need to run OpenMV IDE using the ``openmvide.sh`` "
"script if you've installed Qt on linux. The ``openmvide.sh`` script fixes"
" linker path issues before launching OpenMV IDE to make sure that it runs"
" on any system."
msgstr ""
"一般来说，如果您在 Linux 上安装了 Qt，那么您需要使用 ``openmvide.sh`` "
"脚本来运行 OpenMV IDE。``openmvide.sh`` 脚本在启动 OpenMV IDE "
"之前修复了链接器路径问题，以确保它在任何系统上运行。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/software_setup.rst:77
msgid "Linux-RaspberryPi"
msgstr "Linux-RaspberryPi"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/software_setup.rst:79
msgid ""
"OpenMV IDE comes inside of an installer ``.tar.gz`` file. Just extract "
"the contents where you like (like ``~/openmvide``). Afterwards, see the "
"``README.txt`` file and the ``setup.sh`` file in the output directory for"
" installing device firmware update (DFU) support so that you can recover "
"your OpenMV Cam if you encounter a problem with our boot-loader."
msgstr ""
"OpenMV IDE 包含在一个安装程序 ``.tar.gz`` "
"文件中。只需将内容解压到您喜欢的位置（如 ``~/openmvide``）。安装完成后，"
"请查看输出目录中的 ``README.txt`` 文件和 ``setup.sh`` "
"文件，以安装设备固件更新（DFU）支持，"
"以便在遇到我们的引导加载程序问题时可以恢复您的 OpenMV Cam。"
